      <title>中国股市平淡的重新开放给北京增加了采取更多行动的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/china-stocks-struggle-to-gain-at-reopen-despite-upbeat-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股市在农历新年假期后重新开盘，但涨幅没有投资者预期的那么大，这表明仅靠强劲的旅游和支出数据不足以消除对整体经济的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/china-stocks-struggle-to-gain-at-reopen-despite-upbeat-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 01:44:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
